Package org.jcatapult.deployer.domain

This package contains all domain objects used by the org.jcatapult.deployer.service services

See:
          Description

Class Summary
BaseUserInfo Bean that contains user info for JSCH integration
Deploy Bean to model deployment properties defined in the deploy xml configuration file
DeploymentInfo Bean that contains the information needed by the deploy.groovy script to deploy the archive resource to the selected domain environemnt
Domain Bean models a domain descriptor in the deploy xml configuration file
Environment Bean that models the environment descriptor defined in the deploy xml configuration file
Project Bean to represent a project xml file.
SSHOptions data struct to represent ssh options for the SSHExec and SCP JSCH adapters
 

Package org.jcatapult.deployer.domain Description

This package contains all domain objects used by the org.jcatapult.deployer.service services
